data.value: Hello, I am Omar Faruk. I am a cleaner at a local school. Currently I had an accident and I lost one of my legs. I am going to have a surgery and do the treatments to add an artificial leg. For that, I need a lot of money. I have managed half of the money. I need help for the rest worth 3000 dollars. I have attached my medical reports and bills fyi.
